	The euro was quoted at $1.0591, up from $1.0574 Monday.  
</P>
<P>
	Other dollar rates compared with late Monday: 122.85 Japanese  
yen, down from 123.82; 1.4997 Swiss francs, down from 1.5147; and 
1.4593 Canadian dollars, up from 1.4582 
</P>
