<HEADLINE>  Barak Picks Likud As Likely Partner </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	HERZLIYA, Israel (AP) -- A week after beating it at the polls,  
Ehud Barak's Labor Party named the hard-line Likud as its preferred 
