<HEADLINE> AP Names Kurt Correspondent in Tulsa </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	TULSA, Okla. (AP) -- Kelly Kurt, a newswoman for The Associated  
Press in Tulsa, has been promoted to correspondent in charge of the 
bureau. 
</P>
<P>
	The appointment was announced Tuesday by Oklahoma Chief of  
Bureau Lindel Hutson. 
</P>
